{"about_the_game":"You wake up in a daze in a small village and can't remember anything.<br />\r\nA penguin called Otto tells you that he found you during a snowstorm.<br />\r\nHe was afraid that you wouldn't survive. You learn that many of the penguins are ill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey tell you about the mysterious disease called freezing fever. You want to help the penguins make a healing potion to make the sick penguins healthy again. But to do this, you need 4 different herbs that grow on distant lands.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut where are these lands?<br />\r\nAnd how do you get there?<br />\r\nYou find out that one of these herbs, called frost blossom, only grows here in the cold snowy landscape. But the penguins don't know exactly where it grows.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou set off in search of other settlements to find out if they know the place where the herb you need can be found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd that's where your adventure begins ...","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1727360556","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410940/page.bg.jpg?t=1727360556","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1727360556","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2410940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1727360556","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Family Sharing","id":62}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"You wake up in a daze in a small village and can't remember anything.<br />\r\nA penguin called Otto tells you that he found you during a snowstorm.<br />\r\nHe was afraid that you wouldn't survive. You learn that many of the penguins are ill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey tell you about the mysterious disease called freezing fever. You want to help the penguins make a healing poti